name: Cardio
description: Any type of exercise that gets your heart rate up and keeps it up for a prolonged period of time

name: HIIT
description: A type of interval training exercise

name: Strength Training
description: The use of resistance to muscular contraction to build strength, anaerobic endurance and size of skeletal muscles

name: Bodyweight Training
description: A type of strength-training where you use your own weight to provide resistance against gravity

name: Low Impact
description: Involving a physical activity (such as walking, swimming, or bicycling) in which the body makes gentle contact or no contact with the ground
